{
    "text": "Motown",
    "created": "Fri, 26 Aug 2022 01:35:18 GMT",
    "type": "outline",
    "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/KenSmith/2022/08/25/013518.html?title=motown",
    "subs": [
        {
            "text": "We walked from home to downtown this evening, about a 25 minute journey. Halfway there we could see a band setting up and audience starting to assemble on the gentle grassy slope near the river. We'll check back after dinner. We grabbed a table on the sidewalk at one of the primo corner locations downtown. Though it's gone through a few different ownerships and styles of food, it's usually a good place, with lots of people-watching as a bonus. The outdoor speaker was playing 70s pop, inflected toward Motown, and the red beans and rice dish was tasty.",
            "created": "Fri, 26 Aug 2022 01:35:23 GMT",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/KenSmith/2022/08/25/013518.html?title=motown#a013523"
        },
        {
            "text": "On the way back, we sat on the lawn for several songs by a six-piece, two-singer Motown band, bouncy covers from all the big names. Sitting ahead of us on the lawn, people of different generations were moving to the beat, often in the style of their generation's high school dances. Up front, couples danced and everybody clapped after each song. Messages of love and longing, messages of injustice, carried on the air. \"How long has this been going on?\" An acquaintance stopped by, plopped down on the grass beside us and talked Indiana politics.",
            "created": "Fri, 26 Aug 2022 01:42:12 GMT",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/KenSmith/2022/08/25/013518.html?title=motown#a014212"
        },
        {
            "text": "Back in the neighborhood, the sky was nearly dark and the field lights were on across the street. A high school girls soccer game was underway, uniforms bright red for Adams and white for the visitors. I stood at the fence, where I could see a serious goalkeeper watching the play unfold, moving up and back, calling out instructions to defenders, and from time to time clearing the ball out of their end with full-body torque on the kick.",
            "created": "Fri, 26 Aug 2022 01:41:49 GMT",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/KenSmith/2022/08/25/013518.html?title=motown#a014149"
        },
        {
            "text": "Small city Thursday, good things being done pretty well. Maybe there'd be a fancier offering down the road in Chicago, but we couldn't have walk to the evening's destinations there.",
            "created": "Fri, 26 Aug 2022 01:45:04 GMT",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/KenSmith/2022/08/25/013518.html?title=motown#a014504"
        }
    ]
